		<title>shop kid</title>
		<titleShort>shop kid</titleShort>
		<description>From a young age, [PAWN_nameDef] helped [PAWN_possessive] parents run the family shop. [PAWN_pronoun] would run around organizing stock and attracting customers while [PAWN_possessive] parents worked the counter.</description>
